      "fn_code": "static int\nhardwire_flush_output (struct serial *scb)\n{\n#ifdef HAVE_TERMIOS\n  return tcflush (scb->fd, TCOFLUSH);\n#endif\n\n#ifdef HAVE_TERMIO\n  return ioctl (scb->fd, TCFLSH, 1);\n#endif\n\n#ifdef HAVE_SGTTY\n  /* This flushes both input and output, but we can't do better.  */\n  return ioctl (scb->fd, TIOCFLUSH, 0);\n#endif\n}",
